# CrowdFunding MERN Platform

This is a full-stack crowdfunding web application built using the **MERN stack** (MongoDB, Express.js, React, Node.js).

## ğŸš€ Features

- User authentication (JWT-based)
- Admin and user dashboards
- Create, edit, delete crowdfunding campaigns
- Donation tracking
- Responsive UI (built with React + Tailwind CSS)
- MongoDB backend for storing campaign and user data

## ğŸ“¦ Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** React.js, Tailwind CSS
- **Backend:** Node.js, Express.js
- **Database:** MongoDB
- **Authentication:** JWT

